{
  "video_id": "XewnyUJgyA4",
  "title": "Is war between China and the US inevitable? | Graham Allison",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13548.0,
      "end_time": 17286.0,
      "text": "So, let me thank you for the opportunity to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17310.0,
      "end_time": 22378.0,
      "text": "the biggest international story of your professional lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22402.0,
      "end_time": 26303.0,
      "text": "which is also the most important international challenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26327.0,
      "end_time": 29490.0,
      "text": "the world will face for as far as the eye can see."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29514.0,
      "end_time": 31653.0,
      "text": "The story, of course, is the rise of China."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32106.0,
      "end_time": 35915.0,
      "text": "Never before have so many people risen so far so fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35939.0,
      "end_time": 37750.0,
      "text": "on so many different dimensions."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38336.0,
      "end_time": 42860.0,
      "text": "The challenge is the impact of China&#39;s rise --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42497.0,
      "end_time": 46775.0,
      "text": "the discombobulation this will cause the Unites States"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46800.0,
      "end_time": 48593.0,
      "text": "and the international order,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48617.0,
      "end_time": 52897.0,
      "text": "of which the US has been the principal architect and guardian."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54109.0,
      "end_time": 58152.0,
      "text": "The past 100 years have been what historians now call an \"American Century.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 58568.0,
      "end_time": 61680.0,
      "text": "Americans have become accustomed to their place"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 61930.0,
      "end_time": 63110.0,
      "text": "at the top of every pecking order."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 63862.0,
      "end_time": 66776.0,
      "text": "So the very idea of another country"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66800.0,
      "end_time": 70815.0,
      "text": "that could be as big and strong as the US -- or bigger --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70839.0,
      "end_time": 74759.0,
      "text": "strikes many Americans as an assault on who they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78212.0,
      "end_time": 82633.0,
      "text": "For perspective on what we&#39;re now seeing in this rivalry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 82657.0,
      "end_time": 86323.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s useful to locate it on the larger map of history."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 87890.0,
      "end_time": 90831.0,
      "text": "The past 500 years have seen 16 cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 90855.0,
      "end_time": 94283.0,
      "text": "in which a rising power threatened to displace a ruling power."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 94918.0,
      "end_time": 97476.0,
      "text": "Twelve of those ended in war."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 99434.0,
      "end_time": 105831.0,
      "text": "So just in November, we&#39;ll all pause to mark the 100th anniversary"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 105855.0,
      "end_time": 110363.0,
      "text": "of the final day of a war that became so encompassing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 110387.0,
      "end_time": 114699.0,
      "text": "that it required historians to create an entirely new category: world war."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 115720.0,
      "end_time": 119345.0,
      "text": "So, on the 11th hour of the 11th day"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 119369.0,
      "end_time": 123610.0,
      "text": "of the 11th month in 1918,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 123850.0,
      "end_time": 126267.0,
      "text": "the guns of World War I fell silent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 126291.0,
      "end_time": 130370.0,
      "text": "but 20 million individuals lay dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 132511.0,
      "end_time": 134932.0,
      "text": "I know that this is a sophisticated audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 134956.0,
      "end_time": 136947.0,
      "text": "so you know about the rise of China."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 137403.0,
      "end_time": 141815.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to focus, therefore, on the impact of China&#39;s rise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 141839.0,
      "end_time": 145196.0,
      "text": "on the US, on the international order"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 145220.0,
      "end_time": 147633.0,
      "text": "and on the prospects for war and peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 148402.0,
      "end_time": 150545.0,
      "text": "But having taught at Harvard over many years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 150569.0,
      "end_time": 154570.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve learned that from time to time, it&#39;s useful to take a short pause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 154594.0,
      "end_time": 157230.0,
      "text": "just to make sure we&#39;re all on the same page."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 157254.0,
      "end_time": 159602.0,
      "text": "The way I do this is, I call a time-out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 159626.0,
      "end_time": 163117.0,
      "text": "I give students a pop quiz -- ungraded, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 163141.0,
      "end_time": 165646.0,
      "text": "So, let&#39;s try this. Time-out, pop quiz."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 166173.0,
      "end_time": 167783.0,
      "text": "Question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 167807.0,
      "end_time": 172506.0,
      "text": "forty years ago, 1978, China sets out on its march to the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 173140.0,
      "end_time": 178500.0,
      "text": "At that point, what percentage of China&#39;s one billion citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 178290.0,
      "end_time": 182174.0,
      "text": "were struggling to survive on less than two dollars a day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 182704.0,
      "end_time": 184634.0,
      "text": "Take a guess -- 25 percent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 186410.0,
      "text": "Fifty?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 187530.0,
      "end_time": 188203.0,
      "text": "Seventy-five?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 189998.0,
      "end_time": 191148.0,
      "text": "Ninety."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 192284.0,
      "end_time": 193483.0,
      "text": "What do you think?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 194895.0,
      "end_time": 196101.0,
      "text": "Ninety."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 196125.0,
      "end_time": 200264.0,
      "text": "Nine out of every 10 on less than two dollars a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 201911.0,
      "end_time": 203817.0,
      "text": "Twenty eighteen, 40 years later."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 204427.0,
      "end_time": 205870.0,
      "text": "What about the numbers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 205895.0,
      "end_time": 207450.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s your bet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 207442.0,
      "end_time": 208592.0,
      "text": "Take a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 213125.0,
      "end_time": 215642.0,
      "text": "Fewer than one in 100 today."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 216498.0,
      "end_time": 219707.0,
      "text": "And China&#39;s president has promised that within the next three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 219731.0,
      "end_time": 222914.0,
      "text": "those last tens of millions will have been raised up"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 222938.0,
      "end_time": 224404.0,
      "text": "above that threshold."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 224958.0,
      "end_time": 227285.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a miracle, actually, in our lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 228188.0,
      "end_time": 229378.0,
      "text": "Hard to believe."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 229402.0,
      "end_time": 232154.0,
      "text": "But brute facts are even harder to ignore."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 233690.0,
      "end_time": 236554.0,
      "text": "A nation that didn&#39;t even appear on any of the international league tables"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 236579.0,
      "end_time": 237895.0,
      "text": "25 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 237919.0,
      "end_time": 239371.0,
      "text": "has soared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 239395.0,
      "end_time": 242664.0,
      "text": "to rival -- and in some areas, surpass -- the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 246964.0,
      "end_time": 250600.0,
      "text": "Thus, the challenge that will shape our world:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 250924.0,
      "end_time": 254418.0,
      "text": "a seemingly unstoppable rising China"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 254442.0,
      "end_time": 259530.0,
      "text": "accelerating towards an apparently immovable ruling US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 259769.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262511.0,
      "text": "on course for what could be the grandest collision in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 264323.0,
      "end_time": 267251.0,
      "text": "To help us get our minds around this challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 267275.0,
      "end_time": 270700.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to introduce you to a great thinker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 271132.0,
      "end_time": 273133.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to present a big idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 273887.0,
      "end_time": 276921.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to pose a most consequential question."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 278244.0,
      "end_time": 280982.0,
      "text": "The great thinker is Thucydides."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 281600.0,
      "end_time": 283320.0,
      "text": "Now, I know his name is a mouthful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 283344.0,
      "end_time": 285462.0,
      "text": "and some people have trouble pronouncing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 285486.0,
      "end_time": 287506.0,
      "text": "So, let&#39;s do it, one, two, three, together:"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 287530.0,
      "end_time": 288902.0,
      "text": "Thucydides."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 288927.0,
      "end_time": 291839.0,
      "text": "One more time: Thucydides."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 291863.0,
      "end_time": 293529.0,
      "text": "So who was Thucydides?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 293942.0,
      "end_time": 296879.0,
      "text": "He was the father and founder of history."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 296903.0,
      "end_time": 299450.0,
      "text": "He wrote the first-ever history book."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 299690.0,
      "end_time": 303180.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s titled \"The History of the Peloponnesian War,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 303204.0,
      "end_time": 306526.0,
      "text": "about the war in Greece, 2500 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 307276.0,
      "end_time": 310466.0,
      "text": "So if nothing else today, you can tweet your friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 310490.0,
      "end_time": 312212.0,
      "text": "\"I met a great thinker."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 312236.0,
      "end_time": 315594.0,
      "text": "And I can even pronounce his name: Thucydides.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 316546.0,
      "end_time": 321244.0,
      "text": "So, about this war that destroyed classical Greece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 321268.0,
      "end_time": 323640.0,
      "text": "Thucydides wrote famously:"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 324561.0,
      "end_time": 331459.0,
      "text": "\"It was the rise of Athens and the fear that this instilled in Sparta"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 331483.0,
      "end_time": 333200.0,
      "text": "that made the war inevitable.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 334618.0,
      "end_time": 336855.0,
      "text": "So the rise of one"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 336879.0,
      "end_time": 339160.0,
      "text": "and the reaction of the other"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 339184.0,
      "end_time": 343183.0,
      "text": "create a toxic cocktail of pride,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 343207.0,
      "end_time": 346100.0,
      "text": "arrogance, paranoia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 346250.0,
      "end_time": 348467.0,
      "text": "that drug them both to war."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 350177.0,
      "end_time": 352800.0,
      "text": "Which brings me to the big idea:"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 353900.0,
      "end_time": 354558.0,
      "text": "Thucydides&#39;s Trap."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 355701.0,
      "end_time": 358982.0,
      "text": "\"Thucydides&#39;s Trap\" is a term I coined several years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 359600.0,
      "end_time": 361592.0,
      "text": "to make vivid Thucydides&#39;s insight."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 362569.0,
      "end_time": 366799.0,
      "text": "Thucydides&#39;s Trap is the dangerous dynamic that occurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 366823.0,
      "end_time": 370656.0,
      "text": "when a rising power threatens to displace a ruling power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 370680.0,
      "end_time": 372404.0,
      "text": "like Athens --"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 372428.0,
      "end_time": 376926.0,
      "text": "or Germany 100 years ago, or China today --"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 376950.0,
      "end_time": 379330.0,
      "text": "and their impact on Sparta,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 379355.0,
      "end_time": 383182.0,
      "text": "or Great Britain 100 years ago, or the US today."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 384205.0,
      "end_time": 386125.0,
      "text": "As Henry Kissinger has said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 386149.0,
      "end_time": 390974.0,
      "text": "once you get this idea, this concept of Thucydides&#39;s Trap in your head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 390998.0,
      "end_time": 392676.0,
      "text": "it will provide a lens"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 392701.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "for helping you look through the news and noise of the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 396284.0,
      "end_time": 398884.0,
      "text": "to understand what&#39;s actually going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 400649.0,
      "end_time": 405450.0,
      "text": "So, to the most consequential question about our world today:"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 406863.0,
      "end_time": 410276.0,
      "text": "Are we going to follow in the footsteps of history?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 411466.0,
      "end_time": 417481.0,
      "text": "Or can we, through a combination of imagination and common sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 417505.0,
      "end_time": 418862.0,
      "text": "and courage"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 418886.0,
      "end_time": 423302.0,
      "text": "find a way to manage this rivalry"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 423326.0,
      "end_time": 426294.0,
      "text": "without a war nobody wants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 426318.0,
      "end_time": 429185.0,
      "text": "and everybody knows would be catastrophic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 430350.0,
      "end_time": 432403.0,
      "text": "Give me five minutes to unpack this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 432427.0,
      "end_time": 437403.0,
      "text": "and later this afternoon, when the next news story pops up for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 437427.0,
      "end_time": 440837.0,
      "text": "about China doing this, or the US reacting like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 440861.0,
      "end_time": 444280.0,
      "text": "you will be able to have a better understanding of what&#39;s going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 444304.0,
      "end_time": 446780.0,
      "text": "and even to explain it to your friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 447678.0,
      "end_time": 452179.0,
      "text": "So as we saw with this flipping the pyramid of poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 452203.0,
      "end_time": 453914.0,
      "text": "China has actually soared."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 454456.0,
      "end_time": 455606.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s meteoric."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 456354.0,
      "end_time": 459417.0,
      "text": "Former Czech president, Vaclav Havel, I think, put it best."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 459441.0,
      "end_time": 464203.0,
      "text": "He said, \"All this has happened so fast, we haven&#39;t yet had time to be astonished.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 464228.0,
      "end_time": 466648.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 466672.0,
      "end_time": 470442.0,
      "text": "To remind myself how astonished I should be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 470466.0,
      "end_time": 474656.0,
      "text": "I occasionally look out the window in my office in Cambridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 474680.0,
      "end_time": 477426.0,
      "text": "at this bridge, which goes across the Charles River,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 477450.0,
      "end_time": 480330.0,
      "text": "between the Kennedy School and Harvard Business School."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 480933.0,
      "end_time": 484864.0,
      "text": "In 2012, the State of Massachusetts said they were going to renovate this bridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 484888.0,
      "end_time": 486443.0,
      "text": "and it would take two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 487530.0,
      "end_time": 489520.0,
      "text": "In 2014, they said it wasn&#39;t finished."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 490410.0,
      "end_time": 493339.0,
      "text": "In 2015, they said it would take one more year."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 493363.0,
      "end_time": 495141.0,
      "text": "In 2016, they said it&#39;s not finished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 495165.0,
      "end_time": 498400.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not going to tell you when it&#39;s going to be finished."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 498400.0,
      "end_time": 501168.0,
      "text": "Finally, last year, it was finished -- three times over budget."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 502307.0,
      "end_time": 507815.0,
      "text": "Now, compare this to a similar bridge that I drove across last month in Beijing."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 507839.0,
      "end_time": 509587.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called the Sanyuan Bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 510284.0,
      "end_time": 513939.0,
      "text": "In 2015, the Chinese decided they wanted to renovate that bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 513964.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516638.00000000006,
      "text": "It actually has twice as many lanes of traffic."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 517354.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520950.00000000006,
      "text": "How long did it take for them to complete the project?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 520663.0,
      "end_time": 522414.0,
      "text": "Twenty fifteen, what do you bet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 524649.0,
      "end_time": 526688.0,
      "text": "Take a guess -- OK, three --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 526712.0,
      "end_time": 527997.0,
      "text": "Take a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 532748.0,
      "end_time": 536800.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 540236.0,
      "end_time": 542680.0,
      "text": "The answer is 43 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 542704.0,
      "end_time": 543905.0,
      "text": "(Audience: Wow!)"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 548630.0,
      "end_time": 550658.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 556390.0,
      "end_time": 559172.0,
      "text": "Graham Allison: Now, of course, that couldn&#39;t happen in New York."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 559196.0,
      "end_time": 560753.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 561482.0,
      "end_time": 566653.0,
      "text": "Behind this speed in execution is a purpose-driven leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 566677.0,
      "end_time": 568544.0,
      "text": "and a government that works."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 569657.0,
      "end_time": 572755.0,
      "text": "The most ambitious and most competent leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 572779.0,
      "end_time": 576260.0,
      "text": "on the international stage today is Chinese President Xi Jinping."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 576284.0,
      "end_time": 579410.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s made no secret about what he wants."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 579434.0,
      "end_time": 582410.0,
      "text": "As he said when he became president six years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 582434.0,
      "end_time": 586288.0,
      "text": "his goal is to make China great again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 586312.0,
      "end_time": 588149.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 588173.0,
      "end_time": 592486.0,
      "text": "a banner he raised long before Donald Trump picked up a version of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 593919.0,
      "end_time": 600773.0,
      "text": "To that end, Xi Jinping has announced specific targets for specific dates:"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 600797.0,
      "end_time": 605483.0,
      "text": "2025, 2035, 2049."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 606257.0,
      "end_time": 612577.0,
      "text": "By 2025, China means to be the dominant power"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 612601.0,
      "end_time": 616886.0,
      "text": "in the major market in 10 leading technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 616910.0,
      "end_time": 619934.0,
      "text": "including driverless cars, robots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 619958.0,
      "end_time": 622810.0,
      "text": "artificial intelligence, quantum computing."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 623204.0,
      "end_time": 628750.0,
      "text": "By 2035, China means to be the innovation leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 628100.0,
      "end_time": 630567.0,
      "text": "across all the advanced technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 631427.0,
      "end_time": 635445.0,
      "text": "And by 2049, which is the 100th anniversary"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 635469.0,
      "end_time": 637910.0,
      "text": "of the founding of the People&#39;s Republic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 637934.0,
      "end_time": 640997.0,
      "text": "China means to be unambiguously number one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 641220.0,
      "end_time": 645956.0,
      "text": "including, [says] Xi Jinping, an army that he calls \"Fight and Win.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 647498.0,
      "end_time": 650228.0,
      "text": "So these are audacious goals, but as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 650252.0,
      "end_time": 653339.0,
      "text": "China is already well on its way"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 653363.0,
      "end_time": 654696.0,
      "text": "to these objectives."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 655387.0,
      "end_time": 658161.0,
      "text": "And we should remember how fast our world is changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 659540.0,
      "end_time": 660641.0,
      "text": "Thirty years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 660665.0,
      "end_time": 664120.0,
      "text": "the World Wide Web had not yet even been invented."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 665860.0,
      "end_time": 669795.0,
      "text": "Who will feel the impact of this rise of China most directly?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 670399.0,
      "end_time": 672317.0,
      "text": "Obviously, the current number one."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 673185.0,
      "end_time": 675565.0,
      "text": "As China gets bigger and stronger and richer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 675590.0,
      "end_time": 677590.0,
      "text": "technologically more advanced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 677614.0,
      "end_time": 682428.0,
      "text": "it will inevitably bump up against American positions and prerogatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 683495.0,
      "end_time": 686246.0,
      "text": "Now, for red-blooded Americans --"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 686270.0,
      "end_time": 690683.0,
      "text": "and especially for red-necked Americans like me; I&#39;m from North Carolina --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 690707.0,
      "end_time": 693400.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s something wrong with this picture."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 693689.0,
      "end_time": 696661.0,
      "text": "The USA means number one, that&#39;s who we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 698721.0,
      "end_time": 702664.0,
      "text": "But again, to repeat: brute facts are hard to ignore."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 703673.0,
      "end_time": 707585.0,
      "text": "Four years ago, Senator John McCain asked me to testify about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 707609.0,
      "end_time": 710743.0,
      "text": "to his Senate Armed Services Committee."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 711299.0,
      "end_time": 715360.0,
      "text": "And I made for them a chart that you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 715600.0,
      "end_time": 718108.0,
      "text": "that said, compare the US and China"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 718133.0,
      "end_time": 722649.0,
      "text": "to kids on opposite ends of a seesaw on a playground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 722673.0,
      "end_time": 725696.0,
      "text": "each represented by the size of their economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 725720.0,
      "end_time": 729844.0,
      "text": "As late as 2004, China was just half our size."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 731220.0,
      "end_time": 734886.0,
      "text": "By 2014, its GDP was equal to ours."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 734910.0,
      "end_time": 740218.0,
      "text": "And on the current trajectory, by 2024, it will be half again larger."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 742744.0,
      "end_time": 747293.0,
      "text": "The consequences of this tectonic change will be felt everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 747317.0,
      "end_time": 749609.0,
      "text": "For example, in the current trade conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 749633.0,
      "end_time": 752241.0,
      "text": "China is already the number one trading partner"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 752265.0,
      "end_time": 755577.0,
      "text": "of all the major Asian countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 756776.0,
      "end_time": 759144.0,
      "text": "Which brings us back to our Greek historian."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 760331.0,
      "end_time": 766530.0,
      "text": "Harvard&#39;s \"Thucydides&#39;s Trap Case File\" has reviewed the last 500 years of history"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 766770.0,
      "end_time": 769831.0,
      "text": "and found 16 cases in which a rising power"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 769855.0,
      "end_time": 771785.0,
      "text": "threatened to displace a ruling power."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 772344.0,
      "end_time": 774576.0,
      "text": "Twelve of these ended in war."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 777938.0,
      "end_time": 783231.0,
      "text": "And the tragedy of this is that in very few of these"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 783255.0,
      "end_time": 786350.0,
      "text": "did either of the protagonists want a war;"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 787236.0,
      "end_time": 790538.0,
      "text": "few of these wars were initiated by either the rising power"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 790562.0,
      "end_time": 791921.0,
      "text": "or the ruling power."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 791945.0,
      "end_time": 793633.0,
      "text": "So how does this work?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 793657.0,
      "end_time": 797902.0,
      "text": "What happens is, a third party&#39;s provocation"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 797926.0,
      "end_time": 800379.0,
      "text": "forces one or the other to react,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 801490.0,
      "end_time": 804235.0,
      "text": "and that sets in motion a spiral,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 804259.0,
      "end_time": 807128.0,
      "text": "which drags the two somewhere they don&#39;t want to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 807152.0,
      "end_time": 809342.0,
      "text": "If that seems crazy, it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 809366.0,
      "end_time": 810607.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s life."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 811900.0,
      "end_time": 812695.0,
      "text": "Remember World War I."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 813953.0,
      "end_time": 816814.0,
      "text": "The provocation in that case"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 816839.0,
      "end_time": 820188.0,
      "text": "was the assassination of a second-level figure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 820212.0,
      "end_time": 822137.0,
      "text": "Archduke Franz Ferdinand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 823140.0,
      "end_time": 826204.0,
      "text": "which then led the Austro-Hungarian emperor"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 826228.0,
      "end_time": 828314.0,
      "text": "to issue an ultimatum to Serbia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 828339.0,
      "end_time": 830930.0,
      "text": "they dragged in the various allies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 830117.0,
      "end_time": 832892.0,
      "text": "within two months, all of Europe was at war."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 834823.0,
      "end_time": 838752.0,
      "text": "So imagine if Thucydides were watching planet Earth today."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 838777.0,
      "end_time": 839977.0,
      "text": "What would he say?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 841118.0,
      "end_time": 845959.0,
      "text": "Could he find a more appropriate leading man for the ruling power"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 845983.0,
      "end_time": 847417.0,
      "text": "than Donald J Trump?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 847442.0,
      "end_time": 848807.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 848831.0,
      "end_time": 854690.0,
      "text": "Or a more apt lead for the rising power than Xi Jinping?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 855228.0,
      "end_time": 857236.0,
      "text": "And he would scratch his head"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 857260.0,
      "end_time": 862624.0,
      "text": "and certainly say he couldn&#39;t think of more colorful provocateur"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 862648.0,
      "end_time": 864907.0,
      "text": "than North Korea&#39;s Kim Jong-un."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 866629.0,
      "end_time": 870271.0,
      "text": "Each seems determined to play his assigned part"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 870295.0,
      "end_time": 871829.0,
      "text": "and is right on script."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 873311.0,
      "end_time": 877815.0,
      "text": "So finally, we conclude again with the most consequential question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 877839.0,
      "end_time": 880728.0,
      "text": "the question that will have the gravest consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 880752.0,
      "end_time": 882782.0,
      "text": "for the rest of our lives:"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 885211.0,
      "end_time": 891450.0,
      "text": "Are Americans and Chinese going to let the forces of history drive us to a war"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 891690.0,
      "end_time": 893281.0,
      "text": "that would be catastrophic for both?"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 894990.0,
      "end_time": 897236.0,
      "text": "Or can we summon the imagination and courage"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 897260.0,
      "end_time": 899242.0,
      "text": "to find a way to survive together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 900355.0,
      "end_time": 903362.0,
      "text": "to share the leadership in the 21st century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 903386.0,
      "end_time": 907916.0,
      "text": "or, as Xi Jinping [said], to create a new form of great power relations?"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 908371.0,
      "end_time": 910903.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the issue I&#39;ve been pursuing passionately"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 910927.0,
      "end_time": 912506.0,
      "text": "for the last two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 912530.0,
      "end_time": 915473.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had the opportunity to talk and, indeed, to listen"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 915498.0,
      "end_time": 917656.0,
      "text": "to leaders of all the relevant governments --"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 917680.0,
      "end_time": 921608.0,
      "text": "Beijing, Washington, Seoul, Tokyo --"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 921633.0,
      "end_time": 926186.0,
      "text": "and to thought leaders across the spectrum of both the arts and business."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 926210.0,
      "end_time": 928376.0,
      "text": "I wish I had more to report."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 928400.0,
      "end_time": 932448.0,
      "text": "The good news is that leaders are increasingly aware"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 932472.0,
      "end_time": 934822.0,
      "text": "of this Thucydidean dynamic"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 934846.0,
      "end_time": 936406.0,
      "text": "and the dangers that it poses."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 937227.0,
      "end_time": 939944.0,
      "text": "The bad news is that nobody has a feasible plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 939969.0,
      "end_time": 942103.0,
      "text": "for escaping history as usual."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 943299.0,
      "end_time": 945910.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s clear to me that we need some ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 945934.0,
      "end_time": 949424.0,
      "text": "outside the box of conventional state graph --"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 949919.0,
      "end_time": 953470.0,
      "text": "indeed, from another page or another space --"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 954707.0,
      "end_time": 956929.0,
      "text": "which is what brings me to TED today"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 956953.0,
      "end_time": 959651.0,
      "text": "and which brings me to a request."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 961326.0,
      "end_time": 966695.0,
      "text": "This audience includes many of the most creative minds on the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 966719.0,
      "end_time": 968402.0,
      "text": "who get up in the morning and think"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 968426.0,
      "end_time": 971171.0,
      "text": "not only about how to manage the world we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 971195.0,
      "end_time": 973569.0,
      "text": "but how to create worlds that should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 974633.0,
      "end_time": 979752.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m hopeful that as this sinks in and as you reflect on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 979776.0,
      "end_time": 983805.0,
      "text": "some of you are going to have some bold ideas, actually some wild ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 983829.0,
      "end_time": 987890.0,
      "text": "that when we find, will make a difference in this space."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 987498.0,
      "end_time": 989910.0,
      "text": "And just to remind you if you do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 989934.0,
      "end_time": 991545.0,
      "text": "this won&#39;t be the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 992518.0,
      "end_time": 995480.0,
      "text": "Let me remind you of what happened right after World War II."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 996875.0,
      "end_time": 1000494.0,
      "text": "A remarkable group of Americans and Europeans and others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1000520.0,
      "end_time": 1004261.0,
      "text": "not just from government, but from the world of culture and business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1004280.0,
      "end_time": 1007347.0,
      "text": "engaged in a collective surge of imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1008500.0,
      "end_time": 1011420.0,
      "text": "And what they imagined and what they created"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1011440.0,
      "end_time": 1013814.0,
      "text": "was a new international order,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1014710.0,
      "end_time": 1018496.0,
      "text": "the order that&#39;s allowed you and me to live our lives, all of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1018520.0,
      "end_time": 1020249.0,
      "text": "without great power war"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1021310.0,
      "end_time": 1024539.0,
      "text": "and with more prosperity than was ever seen before on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1025800.0,
      "end_time": 1027470.0,
      "text": "So, a remarkable story."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1028400.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1033931.0000000001,
      "text": "Interestingly, every pillar of this project that produced these results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1033950.0,
      "end_time": 1035540.0,
      "text": "when first proposed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1035569.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1038260.9999999999,
      "text": "was rejected by the foreign policy establishment"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1038280.0,
      "end_time": 1041428.0,
      "text": "as naive or unrealistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1041920.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1043904.0000000001,
      "text": "My favorite is the Marshall Plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1044839.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1047537.9999999999,
      "text": "After World War II, Americans felt exhausted."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1047560.0,
      "end_time": 1049578.0,
      "text": "They had demobilized 10 million troops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1049600.0,
      "end_time": 1052781.0,
      "text": "they were focused on an urgent domestic agenda."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1052810.0,
      "end_time": 1057303.0,
      "text": "But as people began to appreciate how devastated Europe was"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1057270.0,
      "end_time": 1059781.0,
      "text": "and how aggressive Soviet communism was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1059810.0,
      "end_time": 1063730.0,
      "text": "Americans eventually decided to tax themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1063750.0,
      "end_time": 1067563.0,
      "text": "a percent and a half of GDP every year for four years"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1067590.0,
      "end_time": 1071448.0,
      "text": "and send that money to Europe to help reconstruct these countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1071470.0,
      "end_time": 1074319.0,
      "text": "including Germany and Italy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1074340.0,
      "end_time": 1076847.0,
      "text": "whose troops had just been killing Americans."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1077740.0,
      "end_time": 1078890.0,
      "text": "Amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1079790.0,
      "end_time": 1082124.0,
      "text": "This also created the United Nations."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1082150.0,
      "end_time": 1083300.0,
      "text": "Amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1083900.0,
      "end_time": 1086886.0,
      "text": "The Universal Declaration of Human Rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1086910.0,
      "end_time": 1088210.0,
      "text": "The World Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1088230.0,
      "end_time": 1089415.0,
      "text": "NATO."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1089440.0,
      "end_time": 1093341.0,
      "text": "All of these elements of an order for peace and prosperity."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1093360.0,
      "end_time": 1096665.0,
      "text": "So, in a word, what we need to do is do it again."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1097920.0,
      "end_time": 1103781.0,
      "text": "And I think now we need a surge of imagination, creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1103100.0,
      "end_time": 1105270.0,
      "text": "informed by history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1106770.0,
      "end_time": 1110562.0,
      "text": "for, as the philosopher Santayana reminded us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1110590.0,
      "end_time": 1114646.0,
      "text": "in the end, only those who refuse to study history"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1114670.0,
      "end_time": 1116258.0,
      "text": "are condemned to repeat it."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1117870.0,
      "end_time": 1118246.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1118270.0,
      "end_time": 1122201.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}